  "summary": "Discourse has Unauthorized Post Data Exposure in discourse-user-notes",
  "details": "Discourse is an open-source discussion platform. Prior to versions 2026.3.0, 2026.2.1, and 2026.1.2, a moderator could exploit insufficient authorization checks to access metadata of posts they should not have permission to view. Versions 2026.3.0, 2026.2.1, and 2026.1.2 contain a patch.",
